<doc id="213570" wikidata="Q2123647" url="?curid=213570" title="Parszowice">
<text>Parszowice is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Ścinawa, within Lubin County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately south-west of Ścinawa, east of Lubin, and north-west of the regional capital Wrocław.

